openclaw-railway-adaptor
========================

This repository is a Railway deployment adapter for the openclaw project.
It is licensed under the MIT License (see LICENSE).

The Docker image deployed at runtime is the upstream
ghcr.io/openclaw/openclaw image, which is governed by openclaw's own
copyright and license terms:

    OpenClaw — https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw
    License: MIT
    Copyright (c) the openclaw contributors

The upstream LICENSE file is bundled inside the image at /app/LICENSE
(mirrored from https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/LICENSE)
and is preserved on every redistribution by virtue of using the upstream
image as a base.

This adapter repo neither modifies nor redistributes openclaw source code.
It only:
  - References the upstream image by digest in Dockerfile
  - Adds a thin entrypoint (start.sh) for env validation and Railway-friendly
    bind/port flags
  - Provides Railway and GitHub Actions configuration

